g\"></p>\n              </div>\n            </details>\n\n<h2 id=\"创建SSH公钥\"><a href=\"#创建SSH公钥\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建SSH公钥\"></a>创建SSH公钥</h2><ol>\n<li>进入个人账户设置建立SSH公钥，填入在GitHub在本地的<code>id_rsa.pub</code>公钥即可可公用</li>\n</ol>\n<details green><summary> <p>查看图例</p> </summary>\n              <div class='content'>\n              <p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Rr210/image@master/hexo/3/coding_!!.jpeg\"></p>\n              </div>\n            </details>\n\n<h2 id=\"修改本地\"><a href=\"#修改本地\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改本地\"></a>修改本地</h2><ol>\n<li>修改本地的hexo根目录下的_config.yml的<code>deply</code>设置</li>\n</ol>\n<details green><summary> <p>查看图例</p> </summary>\n              <div class='content'>\n              <p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Rr210/image@master/hexo/3/wdaw.jpeg\"></p>\n              </div>\n            </details>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>此链接是你创建的项目仓库地址</li>\n</ol>\n<details green><summary> <p>查看图例</p> </summary>\n              <div class='content'>\n              <p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Rr210/image@master/hexo/3/coding_!wd.jpeg\"></p>\n              </div>\n            </details>\n\n<h2 id=\"本地执行\"><a href=\"#本地执行\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"本地执行\"></a>本地执行</h2><ol>\n<li>修改配置好本地hexo后，尝试测试一下</li>\n<li><code>hexo d</code>或者<code>gulp build</code></li>\n<li><code>注</code>执行过程中会出现验coding的账户信息，填入账号和密码即可，下次部署就不需要填写了</li>\n</ol>\n","categories":[{"name":"技术·教程","path":"api/categories/技术·教程.json"},{"name":"Coding","path":"api/categories/Coding.json"}],"tags":[]}